### Arquivo de testes para API de Pacientes
### Pré-requisito: ter um token JWT válido de um usuário com role DOCTOR

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = seu_jwt_token_aqui

### 1. Criar novo paciente
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "fullName": "João Silva Santos",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "birthDate": "1990-05-15",
  "gender": "Masculino",
  "phone": "(11) 99999-9999",
  "weight": 75.5,
  "height": 1.78
}

### 2. Listar todos os pacientes ativos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Buscar paciente por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Atualizar paciente
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "fullName": "João Silva Santos Junior",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "birthDate": "1990-05-15",
  "gender": "Masculino",
  "phone": "(11) 88888-8888",
  "weight": 76.0,
  "height": 1.78
}

### 5. Inativar paciente
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1/inactive
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Exemplos de respostas esperadas:

